\" id=\"SE-101be519-44aa-474c-ac5e-97e765967842\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4834afef-5f95-4a3f-a62b-2d2fde79a706\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e38ca8d5-4812-4860-bb1d-02682d61f963\" style=\"color:#555555;\">블로그로 만난 대표님 중에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6048b74e-8487-426f-8ab3-7a77583d9eb9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c93d6cbb-adf4-4890-8a32-19f38a17a96a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 캐미가 맞는 대표님이셨습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-64d9c5b1-f685-4c64-8715-234e4dea4846\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:622px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223836146736/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1379b124-8541-4b7b-8278-ab8986db9b43\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-70027dcc-27ce-46dd-9b06-73feb9eb950e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1c9cf87e-298b-423a-aece-6686182f1be5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대표님의 신규 사업의 성공을 위해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-52cea384-277f-405c-9248-d6d1a7b61e61\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8577ffc6-a3c4-4ac6-841d-b7afa8b8f4a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">추후 제 블로그에 홍보 글을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-14ecb4bd-1bbf-4f60-aab9-7e666df51cce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eec2e36a-78f1-4560-87c6-e3fcbc976cca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">올려보겠습니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-04a32279-f9b6-44ca-8210-1e002601ef9c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-35734866-5cc5-4f93-be7f-0dbd1da6481c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">행택 상품이 출시되면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4d82297b-3223-4261-adf9-6d43a7caa45b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ecef9269-b6a0-49b5-8312-88a5c7d6f43f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">꼭 연락을 주신다고 하셨습니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-a0805be6-e0d3-4f89-ad53-646d63ae4ef4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f207d9d-64ca-4438-bfd6-09ccd800ef08\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5f386bbe-20f7-4d1b-bb52-638d2d617cab\" style=\"\">제작 일지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8ac647da-5775-4f1a-a828-0bea8345968c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:806px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223836146736/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f6193fa6-be7c-4462-8279-575e1cc3ff32\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b1844981-4c14-4531-8fb5-847d97e4a977\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53e79d46-e304-4f1e-a715-5d796df1e774\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2025년 4월 2일 수요일 처음으로 카톡 했습니다. 요점은 신규 사업 상품 출시로 인해 행택을 제작하고 싶다는 내용이었습니다. 일단 통화를 요청드렸고 의도와 타깃을 공유했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-55c2838a-e2f9-4fed-a051-2c8ff3cc8e97\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d89e98db-cec0-4691-b3b8-955e5fbe9f6e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0085e47e-0b91-4cde-881e-bbdc74702783\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3435d9ec-d85a-4304-9a97-5dd3010f919d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대표님은 프랑스에서 타투를 배우시고 타투를 기반으로 한 티셔츠를 개발하여 사업을 시작하려고 준비 중이셨습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cc8a16b7-f281-4589-abf4-e1fa5e1c5f39\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56352c9e-8ffc-4f14-8d3a-1f1860fa0a21\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c287e810-5b34-4d89-9919-f16d20e743c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4098af30-76b9-4edb-9cfa-d1bfce492343\" style=\"color:#555555;\">회사 로고는 준비된 로고가 있었습니다. 다만 하단의 글자 스타일을 변경하고 싶으시다는 요청이셨습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6e728e31-8199-4e4b-b17c-928c98c6e87c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:805px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223836146736/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a5e3e30d-dfa4-45e8-94b8-72118bab4784\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c55de374-9bff-4c97-9ef9-64344b2f1702\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a0255d36-655f-460a-9ee8-c2e8ae05d6c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------</span></p><!-- } SE