26720d13be\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0606294b-476e-4807-8d39-d85d757f12d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d226bb7e-f191-48a4-8ff0-9fdbfb0c3b92\" style=\"color:#555555;\">진행과 소통을 하는 동안 행택뿐만 아니라 안내장과 봉투도 의뢰를 받았습니다. 견적을 드렸고 감사하게도 저희와 진행하기로 결정했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-17ac1604-5101-4fc5-ba45-71999a3a70dd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00d15ade-4488-42fd-b29e-ab220fb16f47\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2028f341-cc0b-45bc-84d2-67aabccb5e0c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb57c054-d24f-4282-8d2e-8f34b9bad7d0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입금을 확인하고 디자인 작업을 시작했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line7\" id=\"SE-d971ba5c-04a5-487f-a1bc-74b83aba08c7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line7 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5039e811-b348-403f-bfea-d41d5f76499e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c91803dd-9e10-4cb0-99ef-9559de98bce6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff