ext se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3a73e48d-6ec4-4851-a195-4b2a0b13f643\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d118091-c525-4ca0-9a1b-1a02b40c621c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">첫 번째 소감은 창업아이템이라 수만 장씩 진행하지 않았습니다. 일단 소량 500장을 진행하고 성과에 따라 추가 발주를 진행한다고 하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-88158bff-3618-4dbf-8a29-c10bf7d7efe8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7dcbbc0a-7c4b-4749-a120-e8196e35425a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5d95ade0-acfe-4d94-8124-18e22f348a61\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-254867c7-51d3-41d2-ab8e-7890035099ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-fc7a191e-2d02-4945-a7ec-79f2827168d3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-23cb7a6a-da56-4b48-9114-341911136eb0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>린또레또</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-454788ea-c707-475a-b099-5f092119997f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">라는 거친 느낌의 종이(250g)를 사용하였습니다. 이유는 레트로 감성의 최적의 종이라 추천했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e8ca4191-c8e8-482c-85b7-ccff86f6006e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223836146736/015.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7702c485-e320-4226-80bb-d157c93d0170\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d2f1a59a-3b04-48c0-b6af-0a1f7c8e41e0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-601033c7-c0d0-43e8-bcdb-613109a5c754\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">표면이 약간 거친 느낌이면서 탄력 있는 종이입니다. 다만 표면이 거칠기 때문에 박인쇄가 제한이 있습니다. 박인쇄를 선택하실 경우 이 종이를 선택하지 마십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9ed38af3-65a5-4518-8bde-f7d757592090\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5821c117-da59-4396-8a79-8b6da3cdf584\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6128b547-bf9b-4862-8f9e-00292a9a114b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-41ed9653-d3d8-4ab1-877d-c39c3affb4b7\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">*박인쇄시 띤또레또 종이는 작업이 안될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-e71dcb01-aeb1-43d7-abaf-9a4c01f747f0\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223836146736/016.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223836146736/017.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-848ff514-e40b-43d6-82bd-ab4e5ca8c4dd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a983d0ff-8715-4fbc-b905-5bcdfdc72fe5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-23794f86-a159-43de-afa5-8b756a37d548\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 앞면 로고 부분의 은박 인쇄를 하지 않았습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-18682db3-ce29-41cd-aab6-47a208f9c1b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87f905e9-d33b-4d9d-9bd8-0854a3762076\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-24200e68-3e56-4d7c-9add-9d572c7f56cb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31e39e57-d7a4-49a1-b3bd-481eb08ffaee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">두 번째는 자유로운 귀돌이 모양과 타공 그리고 오시(누름선)으로 작업이 진행되었습니다. 최고의 퀄리티와 정확한 접지를 위해 오시(누름선)로 작업하였으며 사방은 라운드를 돌려 작업하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-64e19b49-8637-47d8-b840-cf526ec5ad37\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8dd4863c-8c4b-46a3-8917-afde638b5e5b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9d990b67-701b-4df3-99b8-64a1a17a7b8d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2106a8f3-6243-4bc4-b317-e95368dae722\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 세 번째는 수량입니다. 수량은 500개로 최저 수량으로 작업했습니다. 디자인을 진행하는 경우 본 작업 전에 반드시 최소 수량으로 견적을 받고 진행하시기를 추천드립니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223836146736#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}